<img src="/images/newicons/book.gif" width="15" height="15" alt="" style="vertical-align: text-top" />
<b>
The Dreams that Haunt
</b>
 <img alt="new" src="/images/new.gif" />
 <font class="small">[<a href="http://www.ralloszek.net/ubbthreads/showthreaded.php?Cat=&amp;Board=rp&amp;Number=1601&amp;page=0&amp;view=collapsed&amp;sb=5&amp;o=&amp;vc=1" target="_new">re: Carezzia</a>]</font> 
<br />
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
&nbsp;
<font class="small">
11/02/01 03:59 PM <i></i> 
</font>
</td>
<td align="right" width="30%">

<table class="tablesurround" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="navigation">

<img src="/images/edit.gif" border="0" alt="Edit post" width="21" height="14" style="vertical-align: text-top" />
